NTFS Emu is a modified version of CIOPFS with a hack
to make readdir return files in alphabetical order, 
emulating the behavior of NTFS under Windows; this allows
Civ5, and other apps requiring Find*Files() to return
files in a specific order to work correctly.

This code is licensed under the GPLv2

CIOPFS is available here: 
http://www.brain-dump.org/projects/ciopfs/
